# Drop hand-drawn / AI-generated house sprite PNGs here.
#
# Naming convention (FINAL_GOAL §K6):
#   <playerSlot>-house.png       e.g. p0-house.png
#   <playerSlot>                  p0..p5 (slot in turn order)
#
# Anchor convention: the house's GROUND LINE (the bottom of the building
# where it meets the iso ground tile) should sit on the BOTTOM CENTER of
# the PNG canvas. The loader uses anchor (0.5, 1.0). Recommended canvas
# size: 192×168 (matches the §K5 native dimensions).
#
# Files dropped here are picked up automatically by loadSpriteWithFallback().
# A PNG at p0-house.png replaces the procedural House rig for player p0
# (door, windows, plaque, etc.). Missing PNG ⇒ procedural rig stays.
# See README.md "Drop in your own art" for details.
